text: "Electric Feel" is a 2008 song by MGMT and is the second single from their debut studio album Oracular Spectacular. It went to number 22 in the United Kingdom, number 21 in Ireland, number 10 in New Zealand, number 7 in Australia and number 53 in Canada. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2008 songs Category:MGMT songs Category:Katy Perry songs Category:Synth rock songs Category:Indie rock songs Category:Psychedelic rock songs Category:Pop rock songs Category:Funk rock songs
